  - `"com.google.devtools.ksp.gradle.KspAATask"`: Mean time reduced from 4.5 seconds to 4.5 seconds.

### 3. Statistical Patterns
- Tasks such as `"com.core.alarm:compileDebugKotlin"` and `"com.core.account:compileDebugKotlin"` showed major improvements, with mean execution times dropping by 35.3% and 28.4% respectively, indicating significant optimizations in these areas.

